228
00:11:32,666 --> 00:11:34,583
- YOU'RE RIGHT,
I DIDN'T.

229
00:11:35,708 --> 00:11:38,333
HUH? WHAT?

230
00:11:38,416 --> 00:11:40,833
- YOUR MATCH WAS QUITE OVER
BEFORE MY ARRIVAL.

231
00:11:43,166 --> 00:11:45,833
THAT FAST GUNMANSHIP,
WORDS FAIL

232
00:11:45,916 --> 00:11:49,083
TO DESCRIBE
ITS GREATNESS.

233
