TO AMUSE HIM

239
00:11:58,333 --> 00:11:59,583
FOR A MOMENT.

240
00:11:59,666 --> 00:12:01,458
- ( grunts )

241
00:12:03,166 --> 00:12:06,083
- YOU SLIME!

242
00:12:06,166 --> 00:12:07,958
- YES, LET IT BURN WITHIN YOU.

243
00:12:08,041 --> 00:12:10,250
