249
00:12:29,625 --> 00:12:31,041
READY?

250
00:12:43,791 --> 00:12:45,250
- ( metal scratches )

251
00:12:45,333 --> 00:12:46,875
- ( grunts )
- ( gunshots )

252
00:12:50,666 --> 00:12:51,625
- H'YAH!

253
00:12:58,208 --> 00:13:00,458
IS THAT ALL YOU GOT?
CAUSE ME REAL HARM! 

254
00:13:00,541 --> 00:13:02,625
- YOU NEVER HEARD OF 
WARRIOR'S COMPASSION?

255
00:13:02,708 --> 00:13:05,708
I CAN'T HIT YOU IN ANY WAY
IF IT'D KILL YOU.

256
00:13:05,791 --> 00:13:07,916
- QUITE THE ARROGANCE.
A REAL EYESORE.

257
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:10,458
