TO SPIRITUAL AWARENESS.

258
00:13:10,541 --> 00:13:13,708
- MY FRIEND, PEOPLE DON'T CHANGE
THEIR WAYS THAT EASILY.

259
00:13:13,791 --> 00:13:16,250
- HA HA! YOU ACTUALLY
THINK WE'RE PEOPLE?

260
00:13:16,333 --> 00:13:17,916
ABSURD!
- HUH?

261
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:20,291
- YOU AND I ARE MEN,
YET NOT <i>OF</i> MEN.

262
00:13:20,375 --> 00:13:23,416
WE ARE DARK,
DIABOLICAL PUPPETS.

263
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:25,375
WHAT WE ARE
ARE DEMONS!

264
00:13:25,458 --> 00:13:26,458
( screams )

265
00:13:26,541 --> 00:13:28,041
- ( metal scratching )
- ( rumbling )

266
00:13:31,250 --> 00:13:33,500
- WOW, WHAT IS THAT?
- I DON'T KNOW,

267
00:13:33,583 --> 00:13:35,416
BUT IT'S DEFINITELY
NOT A GOOD THING.

268
00:13:35,500 --> 00:13:37,916
- YOU'RE RIGHT.
DO YOU THINK IT'S VASH?

269
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:40,208
WE'VE GOT TO HELP HIM.
LET'S GO!

270
00:13:40,291 --> 00:13:41,708
- WAIT, MERYL!
- HUH?

271
00:13:41,791 --> 00:13:44,041
WHAT'S WRONG?
- WE CAN'T THIS TIME.

272
00:13:44,125 --> 00:13:46,500
MR. VASH SAID IT'S TOO BIG
FOR US TO HANDLE.

273
00:13:46,583 --> 00:13:48,166
THIS IS SERIOUSLY DANGEROUS.

274
00:13:48,250 --> 00:13:50,416
- I'M WELL AWARE
OF THE DANGER, MILLY.

275
00:13:50,500 --> 00:13:51,625
- MERYL!

276
00:13:53,166 --> 00:13:54,875
- ( pants )

277
00:13:54,958 --> 00:13:56,541
