LIKE YOU MEAN IT?!

279
00:13:58,708 --> 00:14:00,583
AH! FIGHT ME!

280
00:14:00,666 --> 00:14:03,791
- ( metal scratches )
- ( groans )

281
00:14:03,875 --> 00:14:05,791
