A HUGE SHOCKWAVE.

282
00:14:05,875 --> 00:14:08,083
WELL, NO BIG DEAL.
NOTHING I CAN'T DODGE.

283
00:14:08,166 --> 00:14:09,875
- H'YAH!

284
00:14:09,958 --> 00:14:11,708
- ( bullets clink )
- CAN'T YOU MAKE

285
00:14:11,791 --> 00:14:13,541
THOSE BULLETS HIT ME, HUH?!

286
00:14:13,625 --> 00:14:14,916
- ( metal scratches )

287
00:14:23,208 --> 00:14:24,583
- HUH?

288
00:14:27,750 --> 00:14:29,333
COME ON, MAMA'S BOY!

289
00:14:30,583 --> 00:14:31,541
- ( gasps )

290
00:14:31,625 --> 00:14:34,000
- COMPASSION IN
THE HEAT OF BATTLE?!

291
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:38,416
- ( groans )

292
00:14:41,958 --> 00:14:44,166
- THIS IS A GROSS
DISAPPOINTMENT.

293
00:14:44,250 --> 00:14:46,416
- ( coughs )

294
00:14:46,500 --> 00:14:48,416
- AH!
( groans )

295
00:14:48,500 --> 00:14:50,000
- I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

296
00:14:50,083 --> 00:14:52,250
VASH THE STAMPEDE,
IS THIS ALL YOU AMOUNT TO?

297
00:14:54,333 --> 00:14:56,166
- I SEE ABSOLUTELY NOTHING.

298
00:14:56,250 --> 00:14:59,916
TELL ME! AT LEAST 
GIVE ME AN ANSWER,

299
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:02,416
TELL ME WHAT YOU'RE SEEING
RIGHT NOW, AT THIS MOMENT!

300
00:15:02,500 --> 00:15:04,791
TELL ME!
- ( groans )

301
00:15:04,875 --> 00:15:08,791
- Legato: DO YOU INTEND TO DIE,
VASH THE STAMPEDE?

302
00:15:08,875 --> 00:15:10,583
- ( gasps )

303
00:15:10,666 --> 00:15:13,166
- THE TIME HAS COME
FOR YOU TO USE IT. 

304
00:15:14,583 --> 00:15:16,500
- ( straining )

305
00:15:16,583 --> 00:15:19,000
- GO AHEAD, USE IT.

306
00:15:19,083 --> 00:15:22,916
- ( strains )
- USE IT.

307
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:25,083
IT'S SOMETHING
ONLY YOU CAN DO.

308
00:15:25,166 --> 00:15:28,750
USE IT! QUICKLY!

309
00:15:28,833 --> 00:15:30,041
- STOP IT, STOP IT!

310
00:15:30,125 --> 00:15:31,250
STOP IT, STOP IT,
STOP IT!

311
00:15:31,333 --> 00:15:32,750
STOP!

312
00:15:32,833 --> 00:15:36,291
- COWARD.  I CANNOT BELIEVE
HE'S BEGGING FOR HIS LIFE. 

313
00:15:37,666 --> 00:15:38,916
( gasps )

314
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:40,541
WHAT? WHAT IS THAT?

315
00:15:45,250 --> 00:15:47,750
- NO, PLEASE DON'T DO THAT.

316
00:15:55,500 --> 00:15:57,458
NOT THE LIGHT!

317
00:16:00,041 --> 00:16:03,541
- OH MY GOD.
- MR. VASH MEANT WHAT HE SAID.

318
00:16:03,625 --> 00:16:04,833
JUST LOOK AT THIS PLACE.

319
00:16:04,916 --> 00:16:07,458
- WHERE IS HE?
WE'VE GOT TO FIND HIM.

320
00:16:07,541 --> 00:16:11,125
( gasping )

321
00:16:12,500 --> 00:16:14,083
- MERYL, WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

322
00:16:14,166 --> 00:16:16,875
- LET GO OF ME! LET GO OF ME
RIGHT NOW, MILLY!

323
00:16:21,541 --> 00:16:23,458
- ( gasping )

324
00:16:23,541 --> 00:16:24,916
- PUT ME DOWN.

325
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,625
MILLY, I WANT TO GO BACK.

326
00:16:26,708 --> 00:16:29,125
WAIT, I HAVE
TO GO BACK THERE.

327
00:16:29,208 --> 00:16:30,958
- ( static )

328
00:16:33,208 --> 00:16:35,125
- WHAT IS THIS
STRANGE PHENOMENON?

329
00:16:35,208 --> 00:16:37,916
IS THIS SOME SORT OF
TWISTED CHRISTIAN SCIENCE?

330
00:16:40,166 --> 00:16:42,083
( gasps )

331
00:16:42,166 --> 00:16:44,291
- ( screams )

332
00:16:44,375 --> 00:16:46,791
( strains )

333
00:16:50,666 --> 00:16:52,916
STOP, STOP IT NOW!

334
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:55,208
AH! STOP IT!

335
00:16:58,333 --> 00:17:01,000
- WHAT IS THIS
INDESCRIBABLE HORROR

336
00:17:01,083 --> 00:17:02,958
COURSING THROUGH
MY ENTIRE BODY? 

337
00:17:04,083 --> 00:17:05,583
IS THIS IT?

338
00:17:05,666 --> 00:17:08,083
IS THIS THE MOMENT
I'VE BEEN SEEKING?

339
00:17:10,250 --> 00:17:13,000
WILL I REALLY REACH 
SPIRITUAL AWARENESS?

340
00:17:15,750 --> 00:17:18,625
NO! THIS THING BEFORE ME--

341
00:17:18,708 --> 00:17:21,125
- RUN! RUN AWAY NOW!

342
00:17:21,208 --> 00:17:23,583
- ( pants )

343
00:17:23,666 --> 00:17:26,375
( screams )

344
00:17:26,458 --> 00:17:28,166
- RUN!

345
00:17:28,250 --> 00:17:29,625
- WHAT? WHAT IS THAT?!

346
00:17:29,708 --> 00:17:32,208
I DON'T UNDERSTAND!
WHAT THE HELL IS THAT THING!

347
00:17:34,958 --> 00:17:36,750
- STOP IT! STOP IT!
- ( charge builds )

348
00:17:36,833 --> 00:17:38,958
PLEASE, STOP IT!
- ( gunfire )

349
00:17:39,041 --> 00:17:42,291
- ( screaming )
- ( gunfire continues )

350
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:45,916
- ( screams echo )

351
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:47,416
- WHAT THE--

352
00:17:47,500 --> 00:17:49,958
- ( high-pitched whistle )

353
00:17:51,041 --> 00:17:54,208
- ( silence )

354
00:17:56,541 --> 00:17:58,375
( silence continues )

355
00:17:59,500 --> 00:18:02,333
- ( rumbling )

356
00:18:12,541 --> 00:18:14,583
- WHAT IS THAT
HORRIFIC LIGHT?

357
00:18:14,666 --> 00:18:17,208
IS HE THE ONE CREATING THAT?
VASH THE STAMPEDE?

358
00:18:17,291 --> 00:18:19,125
- YES, THIS IS
THE SECOND TIME.

359
00:18:19,208 --> 00:18:22,958
THE FIRST WAS A GREAT EXPLOSION
WHICH TOOK JULY 23 YEARS AGO.

360
00:18:23,041 --> 00:18:24,375
( chuckles )

361
00:18:24,458 --> 00:18:25,625
( slurps )

362
00:18:25,708 --> 00:18:28,583
- MILLY, PLEASE LET ME GO.
I HAVE TO GO BACK.

363
00:18:28,666 --> 00:18:31,250
- I CAN'T DO THAT.
BESIDES, IF YOU DIE,

364
00:18:31,333 --> 00:18:33,583
YOU'LL NEVER SEE HIM AGAIN.
- ( gasps )

365
00:18:42,166 --> 00:18:45,083
- ( both scream )
- ( wind rushes )

366
00:18:48,250 --> 00:18:50,291
- MERYL, LOOK!
- ( gasps )

367
00:18:59,583 --> 00:19:01,875
A HOLE IN THE MOON.

368
00:19:15,375 --> 00:19:18,333
- ( ragged breathing )

369
00:19:20,541 --> 00:19:22,916
I FELT THE TERROR.

370
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:26,458
- Wolfwood: ONLY YOU CAN
SURVIVE SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

371
00:19:26,541 --> 00:19:27,916
- ( grunts )

372
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:30,041
WHO-- WHO ARE YOU?

373
00:19:30,125 --> 00:19:32,083
- WHAT HAPPENED TO
VASH THE STAMPEDE?

374
00:19:32,166 --> 00:19:34,250
- I DON'T KNOW.

375
00:19:34,333 --> 00:19:35,666
- DAMN.

376
00:19:35,750 --> 00:19:37,666
- IF WE ACT QUICKLY,

377
00:19:37,750 --> 00:19:39,250
WE MAY BE ABLE
TO DEFEAT THAT MAN,

378
00:19:39,333 --> 00:19:40,916
THAT HORRIBLE
DEVIL OF A MAN.

379
00:19:41,000 --> 00:19:43,250
VASH THE STAMPEDE
IS TOO DANGEROUS 

380
00:19:43,333 --> 00:19:45,541
TO BE LEFT ALIVE.
IF YOU HELP ME,

381
00:19:45,625 --> 00:19:47,083
WE CAN DO THIS TOGETHER.
- I CAN'T DO THAT.

382
00:19:47,166 --> 00:19:48,625
- ( gun cocks )
- HUH? ARE YOU INSANE?

383
00:19:48,708 --> 00:19:49,666
WHAT'S THE MATTER
WITH YOU?

384
00:19:49,750 --> 00:19:51,541
YOU AND I ARE-- WE COULD--

385
00:19:51,625 --> 00:19:52,833
- I'M SORRY.

386
00:19:56,541 --> 00:20:00,208
SURE, NOBODY DIED
FROM THE BLAST,

387
00:20:00,291 --> 00:20:03,000
BUT JUST LOOK AT THIS.
( blows smoke )

388
00:20:03,083 --> 00:20:04,958
ANOTHER TOWN IN RUBBLE.

389
00:20:05,041 --> 00:20:07,208
IS THIS THE PATH
YOU HAVE CHOSEN?

390
00:20:07,291 --> 00:20:09,583
IS THIS IT,
VASH THE STAMPEDE?

391
00:20:15,750 --> 00:20:17,916
- Man #4: HEY, DID YOU
HEAR THE RUMOR?

392
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:21,000
ABOUT HOW THE HUMANOID TYPHOON
SHOWED UP IN AUGUSTA?

393
00:20:21,083 --> 00:20:22,583
- Man #5: I SURE DID.

394
00:20:22,666 --> 00:20:24,500
YOU KNOW, THEY SAY
HE MANAGED TO DESTROY

395
00:20:24,583 --> 00:20:26,833
THE ENTIRE CITY
ALL BY HIMSELF.

396
00:20:26,916 --> 00:20:29,416
FIRST JULY AND NOW AUGUSTA.

397
00:20:29,500 --> 00:20:31,416
WHAT IN THE HELL
CAN THAT MANIAC BE THINKING?

398
00:20:31,500 --> 00:20:33,583
HE'S COMPLETELY
OUT OF CONTROL.

399
00:20:33,666 --> 00:20:34,916
IT'S JUST GETTING
OUT OF HAND.

400
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:37,708
THE BOUNTY ON HIS HEAD
WILL ONLY GET BIGGER NOW.

401
00:20:37,791 --> 00:20:39,958
AND WHO'S TO SAY HE WON'T
DESTROY OUR TOWN

402
00:20:40,041 --> 00:20:41,416
AND ANY OTHERS?

403
00:20:41,500 --> 00:20:42,791
- Man #4: I'M STARTING
TO BELIEVE IT'S ALL HIS FAULT

404
00:20:42,875 --> 00:20:44,291
THAT WE'RE STUCK
ON THIS PLANET. 

405
00:20:44,375 --> 00:20:47,291
NOT TO MENTION ALL OF THE
OTHER CRAP I'VE HEARD ABOUT HIM.

406
00:20:47,375 --> 00:20:49,083
BUT THERE'S MORE.
THEY'RE SAYING NOW

407
00:20:49,166 --> 00:20:50,708
THAT HE'S ALSO
SOLELY RESPONSIBLE

408
00:20:50,791 --> 00:20:52,541
FOR THAT BIG
HOLE IN THE MOON.

409
00:20:52,625 --> 00:20:54,250
IT MAKES ME SICK
JUST TO THINK ABOUT IT.

410
00:20:54,333 --> 00:20:56,125
- Man #6: WHAT ARE YOU NUTS?
THERE ISN'T A MAN ALIVE

411
00:20:56,208 --> 00:20:58,041
WHO CAN PULL OFF
A STUNT LIKE THAT.

412
00:20:58,125 --> 00:20:59,500
- Man #4: COOL YOUR JETS,
WILL YOU?

413
00:20:59,583 --> 00:21:01,083
I'M JUST TELLING YOU
WHAT I HEARD.

414
00:21:01,166 --> 00:21:04,083
I'M NOT MAKING IT UP.
- Man #6: HEY, AT THIS POINT,

415
00:21:04,166 --> 00:21:05,708
MAYBE WE SHOULD JUST
BE THANKFUL

416
00:21:05,791 --> 00:21:07,833
THAT WE'RE ALL STILL ALIVE.
- Man #5: YEAH,

417
00:21:07,916 --> 00:21:09,458
YOU SAID IT.

418
00:21:13,916 --> 00:21:17,083
- ( cries )

419
00:21:17,166 --> 00:21:18,375
- ( door opens )

420
00:21:18,458 --> 00:21:20,416
- UM, MERYL,
WE RECEIVED A LETTER

421
00:21:20,500 --> 00:21:21,500
FROM THE MAIN OFFICE.

422
00:21:21,583 --> 00:21:23,375
- IT'S ABOUT TIME.

423
00:21:23,458 --> 00:21:25,875
WELL, THEIR CORRESPONDENCE
CERTAINLY IS SLOW.

424
00:21:25,958 --> 00:21:27,833
WE'VE BEEN SITTING HERE
WAITING FOR TWO WEEKS. 

425
00:21:30,083 --> 00:21:31,833
"MERYL STRYFE
AND MILLY THOMPSON

426
00:21:31,916 --> 00:21:36,041
ARE TO RETURN TO
THE MAIN OFFICE IMMEDIATELY.

427
00:21:36,125 --> 00:21:39,250
FURTHERMORE, IN A CONFERENCE
HELD THE OTHER DAY,

428
00:21:39,333 --> 00:21:41,208
IT WAS DECIDED THAT
VASH THE STAMPEDE

429
00:21:41,291 --> 00:21:43,666
WILL BE DESIGNATED AS
MANKIND'S FIRST OFFICIAL

430
00:21:43,750 --> 00:21:45,875
HUMAN DISASTER.

431
00:21:45,958 --> 00:21:47,750
FROM THIS DAY FORWARD,

432
00:21:47,833 --> 00:21:49,500
NO MATTER WHAT KIND 
OF DAMAGE HE CAUSES,

433
00:21:49,583 --> 00:21:51,833
THE BERNADELLI
INSURANCE SOCIETY

434
00:21:51,916 --> 00:21:53,166
WILL BE--"

435
00:21:53,250 --> 00:21:55,500
"WILL BE--"

436
00:21:55,583 --> 00:21:58,000
"WILL BE...

437
00:22:00,541 --> 00:22:03,625
UNINVOLVED."

438
00:22:07,500 --> 00:22:09,416
THIS CAN'T BE.
( cries )

439
00:22:09,500 --> 00:22:10,583
THIS CAN'T BE.

440
00:22:10,666 --> 00:22:13,041
WHAT DO THEY THINK WILL CHANGE

441
00:22:13,125 --> 00:22:15,041
