442
00:22:15,125 --> 00:22:16,875
( cries )
- OH, MERYL.

443
00:22:20,041 --> 00:22:22,916
- ( sobbing wails )

444
00:22:24,333 --> 00:22:26,375
- MR. VASH, YOU'RE A JERK.

445
00:22:26,458 --> 00:22:28,541
YOU MADE MERYL CRY.

446
00:22:28,625 --> 00:22:31,500
I'LL NEVER
EVER FORGIVE YOU FOR THIS.

447
00:22:37,666 --> 00:22:39,875
- ( wind rushes )

448
00:22:42,250 --> 00:22:44,500
- ( theme music plays )

449
00:22:51,083 --> 00:22:53,166
