450
00:24:13,541 --> 00:24:16,375
- Young Vash:
REM TOLD ME

451
00:24:16,458 --> 00:24:18,500
THAT SOMEONE SHE LOVED
DIED ON EARTH.

452
00:24:18,583 --> 00:24:20,750
