454
00:24:23,000 --> 00:24:24,625
WHAT DOES IT FEEL LIKE

455
00:24:24,708 --> 00:24:26,708
TO HAVE SOMEONE YOU LOVE
DIE?

456
00:24:26,791 --> 00:24:28,833
I TRIED THINKING OF
WHAT IT WOULD BE LIKE

457
00:24:28,916 --> 00:24:30,375
IF REM DIED.

458
00:24:30,458 --> 00:24:32,750
WHEN I DID, HOT WATER
CAME OUT OF MY EYES

459
00:24:32,833 --> 00:24:34,750
AND IT WOULDN'T STOP
FOR A LONG TIME.

460
00:24:34,833 --> 00:24:38,791
REM, I'LL ALWAYS 
BE THERE FOR YOU.

461
00:24:38,875 --> 00:24:41,041
I WON'T LEAVE YOU ALONE.

